=== 2.0.0 2014-10-16

* Refactored Collection related methods into it's own class.
* Restructured the library.
* Divided models/validators from core functions.
* Added more tests and coverage.

=== 1.3.2 2014-08-11

* Allowed all API requests to be SSL toggled.

=== 1.3.1 2014-08-08

* Added option to turn SSL off for API calls.

=== 1.3.0 2014-07-30

*** CAUTION: THIS VERSION HAS UPDATED METHODS THAT MAKE PREVIOUS FUNCTION CALLS OBSOLETE ***
* Jumped from 1.1 to 1.3 to match other libraries.
* Added personal stream and timeline support.
* Added create_collection method.
* Updated majority of API calls to use SSL.
* Updated checksum formula to match other libraries.
* Refactored core objects.
* Updated create_collection_meta to take in a dict of optional params.


=== 1.1.4 2014-05-07

* Added rating, counting as acceptable types.
* Removed stream_type as it was no longer needed.

=== 1.1.3 2014-04-23

* Renamed stream to s_type.
* Added checks to make sure that type is of a recognized type.
* Added support for legacy variable stream_type.

=== 1.1.2 2014-04-10

* Fixed url validator.
* Added utility class.

=== 1.1.1 2014-04-08

* Moved build_checksum into its method.

=== 1.1.0 2014-04-07

* Added get_collection_id method.
* Added checksum to buildCollectionMetaToken.
* Changed method name from buildLfToken to buildLivefyreToken.

=== 1.0.2 2014-03-19

* Fixed bugs related to python 3 builds.

=== 1.0.1 2014-03-19

* Reorganized modules.
* Added param checks.
* Added initial Livefyre.get_network static call.

=== 1.0.0 2014-03-18

* Initial commit.